data.description: Contract Pending. Showings start Friday 1/26! Location is everything in this charming ranch home on a quiet street - close to interstate, Aksarben dining and shopping - all just minutes away. Enjoy being just steps from hitchcock park and all it has to offer.  The Chef's kitchen with newer appliances would be impressive in a home twice the size.  Enjoy the generous back patio in a flat and fenced backyard - perfect for entertaining. Two bedrooms up with an updated full bathroom. Downstairs you'll find a large bedroom an updated 3/4th bathroom with plenty of storage. No maintenance siding and newer HVAC make the home even more move in ready. Don't miss out!
